767
00:56:11,101 --> 00:56:12,932
Here's one for the Black Douglas.

768
00:56:13,103 --> 00:56:15,196
Bosie, for God's sake!

769
00:56:15,305 --> 00:56:16,932
And one for his liver!
One for his lights!

770
00:56:17,107 --> 00:56:19,769
One for his stinking rotten soul!

771
00:56:23,313 --> 00:56:25,975
I'll save one for myself.

772
00:56:26,149 --> 00:56:30,142
My own father--
