773
00:56:45,068 --> 00:56:48,697
My life is everything
I ever wanted.

774
00:56:48,872 --> 00:56:50,464
I have fame.

775
00:56:52,041 --> 00:56:53,508
I have recognition.

776
00:56:54,744 --> 00:56:57,736
