818
01:00:22,885 --> 01:00:26,548
Don't be so pathetic.
I've found you the divinest boy.

819
01:00:26,723 --> 01:00:29,487
- Bosie, you promised Constance--
- Bugger Constance.

820
01:00:29,659 --> 01:00:32,150
I'm not your nanny.
