to empty your chamber pot next.

827
01:00:53,316 --> 01:00:57,309
Well, I emptied your chamber pot.
I looked after you.

828
01:00:57,420 --> 01:00:59,718
Well, I'm not looking after you.
Not now.

829
01:00:59,822 --> 01:01:02,347
You don't interest me.
Not when you're ill.

830
01:01:02,492 --> 01:01:05,120
You're just a boring middle-aged man
with a blocked-up nose.

831
01:01:05,294 --> 01:01:09,424
- Bosie, dearest boy.
- Shut up!

832
01:01:09,532 --> 01:01:13,298
''Dearest boy, darling Bosie.''
