837
01:01:26,282 --> 01:01:27,715
but you know nothing about them.

838
01:01:27,850 --> 01:01:29,545
You're the biggest snob
I've ever met...

839
01:01:29,719 --> 01:01:33,018
and you think you're so daring
because you fuck the occasional boy.

840
01:01:33,122 --> 01:01:35,352
Please, you're killing me.

841
01:01:35,458 --> 01:01:37,187
