849
01:02:09,659 --> 01:02:12,025
and I'll send you the bill.

850
01:02:27,643 --> 01:02:29,008
Drink this.

851
01:02:29,145 --> 01:02:34,242
- It will help your fever.
- He's ashamed of loving men.

852
01:02:37,220 --> 01:02:40,053
His father bullies him,
his mother spoils him...

