my whole family to suicide.

897
01:06:09,165 --> 01:06:12,293
I promise you, I won't let him
hurt you ever again.

898
01:06:12,401 --> 01:06:13,766
I promise.

899
01:06:21,444 --> 01:06:23,742
It's not enough.
I want him stopped.

900
01:06:27,383 --> 01:06:30,784
