in England values my work so highly.

938
01:09:58,761 --> 01:10:00,661
- Well, he's gone away.
- He's gone to the country.

939
01:10:00,829 --> 01:10:02,922
Well, I'm sure
he'll be back soon.

940
01:10:05,734 --> 01:10:10,034
Oscar, look. You couldn't
let us have something, could you?

941
01:10:10,139 --> 01:10:12,972
