You know.

942
01:10:14,310 --> 01:10:16,778
Of course. Of course.

943
01:10:16,912 --> 01:10:19,642
Here's half a sovereign. Now you mind
you take good care of that letter.

944
01:10:19,815 --> 01:10:23,273
