in sonnet form in his new magazine.

945
01:10:24,220 --> 01:10:25,585
For fuck's sake.

946
01:10:29,158 --> 01:10:31,319
It's no good
trying to rent you.

947
01:10:31,427 --> 01:10:34,225
You just laugh at us.

948
01:10:34,396 --> 01:10:36,387
- Here.
- Thank you.

949
01:10:37,499 --> 01:10:40,297
He can be very careless,
Lord Alfred.

950
01:10:42,104 --> 01:10:44,436
What a wonderfully
wicked life you lead.

951
01:10:44,573 --> 01:10:46,939
You boys. You boys.

952
01:10:51,680 --> 01:10:54,513
- Where is he?
- Mr. Wilde is not receiving visitors.

953
01:10:54,683 --> 01:10:57,049
- Where is he?
- He's busy, sir. I cannot--

954
01:10:57,186 --> 01:10:59,780
I wish you would get out of my way.
Get out of my way!

955
01:11:02,258 --> 01:11:04,658
Excuse me, sir,
there's a gentleman--

956
01:11:04,793 --> 01:11:05,919
You!

957
01:11:07,162 --> 01:11:08,390
Listen to me.

958
01:11:10,099 --> 01:11:11,691
You're a bugger!

959
01:11:14,003 --> 01:11:17,234
